claim.claim-text:
12. A drive method for driving a piezoelectric actuator having a piezoelectric element vibrating by application of a drive signal with a specific frequency, said drive method comprising:
detecting a vibrating state of said piezoelectric element;
outputting a detection signal;
detecting resonance of said piezoelectric element due to harmonics of said drive signal;
outputting a harmonics detection signal;
supplying said drive signal to said piezoelectric element while controlling said frequency of said drive signal;
controlling said frequency of said drive signal based on said detection signal when said harmonics detection signal is not outputted from said outputting said harmonics signal and said frequency of said drive signal not based on said detection signal when said harmonics detection signal is outputted from said outputting said harmonics signal.
